{"tid":2013880,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有人說眼是靈魂之窗","createTime":"2020-05-12T14:59:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-12T18:37:32.000Z","uid":193661,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"bbb95de6389212064c8b1d199f08947d314ff5a8","tid":2013880,"uid":193661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T14:59:38.000Z","msg":"當你望着一個人的眼，你會知道他心中的想法，悲傷、失望、憤怒......<br />\n<br />\n------所以我上街時會戴上太陽眼鏡。這樣就沒有人知道我的想法，我也不用猜度別人。<br />\n<br />\n給最真實的自己"},{"pid":"7a85358d215392b6f388130d444d512463e1e787","tid":2013880,"uid":20914,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T15:10:45.000Z","msg":"好中二&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"f52f15097294bdb473d970c38585acd4bd43537a","tid":2013880,"uid":24098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T18:37:32.000Z","msg":"你帶太陽眼鏡就望唔到人地對眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}